        <title>三角恒等式的几何表达</title>
        <link>https://whzecomjm.github.io/p/%E4%B8%89%E8%A7%92%E6%81%92%E7%AD%89%E5%BC%8F%E7%9A%84%E5%87%A0%E4%BD%95%E8%A1%A8%E8%BE%BE/</link>
